=head2 cfg_index

 cfg_index

The main content of the index page. Usually, this will
be a call to C<intermixed_index>, that will show a blog-like
index of story abstracts sorted and classified by date, or a
call to C<grouped_index>, that will show the list of abstracts
classified by topic, with as many abstract per topic as
specified in C<cfg_index_topics>.

=cut
{-intermixed_index}
